alerts.headline: Heavy Heat Stress
alerts.description: Severe Early Warning of HEAVY HEAT STRESS in Southern Golan, in Lower Galilee, in Bet Shean Valley, in Hula Valley, in Izrael Valley, in North Coast, in Centeral and South Coast, in Judean Foothills, in Eastern Negev and in Southern Negev  Eilat Mountai on 25/08 from 11 until 18 LT. For further details: https://ims.gov.il/he/IMSwarnings.
